children.name: alertMessageArguments
children.description: Concatenated set of strings representing the message arguments of the event. Each message argument string is enclosed in double quotes, and there is a comma after the ending double quote of each message argument string, except the last one. Any double quotes found within a message argument string are preprocessed and changed to single quotes.
